OL,3,C'Once-in-a-lifetime event': What is a
OL,4,Cnova explosion and how can I see it?
OL,6,F"It's a once-in-a-lifetime event that
OL,7,Fwill create a lot of new astronomers
OL,8,Fout there, giving young people a
OL,9,Fcosmic event they can observe for
OL,10,Fthemselves," said Dr. Rebekah
OL,11,FHounsell, a assistant research
OL,12,Fscientist.
OL,14,F"It's incredibly exciting to have this
OL,15,Ffront row seat," Dr Hounsell said.
OL,17,FWhen can it be seen?
OL,19,FResearchers say the star's behaviour
OL,20,Fover the past decade mirrors the lead-
OL,21,Fup to the 1946 nova explosion.
