OL,3,C'Once-in-a-lifetime event': What is a
OL,4,Cnova explosion and how can I see it?
OL,6,FIf the pattern continues, it is likely
OL,7,Fwe will see the blast by September
OL,8,F2024 - but we don't know exactly when.
OL,10,FWhen it does happen, it will only be
OL,11,Fvisible for a week.
OL,13,FWhat should we look out for?
OL,15,FT Coronae Borealis is found in the
OL,16,FNorthern Crown, a horseshoe-shaped
OL,17,Fcurve of stars west of the Hercules
OL,18,Fconstellation.
