OL,3,C'Once-in-a-lifetime event': What is a
OL,4,Cnova explosion and how can I see it?
OL,6,FStargazers should look between
OL,7,FArcturus and Vega, the two brightest
OL,8,Fstars in the Northern Hemisphere.
OL,10,FDr Elizabeth Hays, chief of the
OL,11,FAstroparticle Physics Laboratory at
OL,12,FNASA Goddard, said those from across
OL,13,Fthe world will be monitoring the
OL,14,Fstar's behaviour.
OL,16,FShe said: "Citizen scientists and
OL,17,Fspace enthusiasts are always looking
OL,18,Ffor those strong, bright signals that
OL,19,Fidentify nova events and other
OL,20,Fphenomena.
